Text: Re TonightChristine lives in the hills and Im pretty sure I wont get cell service there How bout if I plan on picking you up at If Im going to be later than that Ill leave you a message on your work voicemail Right now Ill try to find a place where my phone works so I can call you At PM you wrote I can wait a little bit But lets coordinate OK Prentice Sellers aasBerkeleyEDU on PM To cc Subject Re Tonight Well if dinner is at I think I can probably pick you up at close to What if its going to be a little later than that Would you rather wait or take Bart At PM you wrote done at can you pick me up id love it check your voicemail too i left a message there Prentice Sellers aasBerkeleyEDU on PM To cc Subject Tonight Are you there Ill be online for the next half hour or so Did you get my message Dinner is at What time are you done with class

Re Wine tastingshould do Navarro Original Message From Nancy Sellers Nancy obertMondavicom To Cameron Jeff Dasovich Prentice Berkeley Prentice Sellers Scott Laughlin Cc Subject Wine tasting For our wine tasting at the dome I am assuming that Cameron and Scott will want to do Byron Pinot and Byron Chard I will probably do RMW Jeff and PP do you have any ideas or requests that I could help you with Nancy phone fax Plus je bois mieux je chante

Niner GameCameron cant go to the game shes in Boston I dont have anyone to go with me My dad is planning on selling the tickets to someone he doesnt even know Do you want to find out if anyone in your family wants to use them He needs to know in the next half hour

Re FW Excel tipsoooooo coooool Original Message From Nancy Sellers Nancy obertMondavicom To Jeff Dasovich Prentice Berkeley Prentice Sellers Cc Subject FW Excel tip Original Message From Lisa Castle Sent Thursday May PM To Nancy Sellers Subject Excel tip My turn to return the favor of the tip you sent to me let me know if youve already heard of this one Here is a tip to change a table of data from whole numbers to s In an empty cell type Select the cell and click Copy on the Edit menu Now select the cells containing the values you want to change On the Edit menu click Paste Special Under Paste click Values and under Operation click Divide Click OK This will work to multiply divide etc If you use and multiply it will change values to negative

Fwd NFL will donate to breast cancer foundation for clicking on their web siteanother example of the NFL doing good works Mom check out these sites too nflforherbeginnerindexhtml nflforherbernshtml Sender Date Tue Oct Subject NFL will donate to breast cancer foundation for clicking on their web site For today only Tues Oct the NFL will donate for every page view on its NFL For Her web page funds will benefit the Komen Foundation Log on to make a difference And yes for me this was my first time on nflcom nflforher

Re Friday is the last day for purchasing Discount Ski Ticketsshould talk to your brother and Tom and see if they want some Since they are transferrable I guess it doesnt hurt to buy them At AM you wrote hi sweetie should we buy some Will C Birdsey aasBerkeleyE To DU Sent by cc owner aasBe Subject Friday is the last day for purchasing Discount Ski rkeleyEDU Tickets PM Please respond to Will C Birdsey Just a quick reminder Friday is the last day to purchase your discount ski tickets We need to buy to make this thing happen Please get your checks in ASAP Thanks aas is organizing discounted ski tickets at Squaw Valley and Alpine Meadows This is a great way to save some money if you plan on skiing this year Both Squaw and Alpine are PREMIERE North Lake Tahoe ski resorts Squaw Valley Tickets cost each and include night skiing Regular Price Make checks payable to Will Birdsey and leave them in my MBA mailbox Deadline Friday October th Alpine Meadows Tickets cost each Regular Price Make checks payable to Matt Hawe and leave them in his MBA mailbox Deadline Friday October th Tickets are good all ski season including holidays and weekends Tickets are transferrable Buy as many or as few tickets as you want See you on the slopes

Re Re did I forgetneed to take the camper shell off Original Message From To Nancy Sellers Nancy obertMondavicom Cc Eldon Sellers Jeff Dasovich Prentice Sellers Prentice Berkeley Subject Re did I forget did i mention that rental fees to use the truck are day that aside our net account is now Nancy owes Jeff for Abalone entree Jeff owes Nancy for parking fees day Nancy owes Jeff Also thanks a million for the delicious dinner the very competitive game of spades letting me do my laundry and compelling conversation about waterynonwatery tomatoes Best Jeff You back at work Nancy Sellers Nancy obertMo To Jeff Dasovich ndavicom cc Eldon Sellers

RE Drunken Brothers Cc that was a hint that thats something we should cook for her At PM wrote BO you hearing any reviews i think it opened this week or last week And I think Camerons got it right you guys on the th me and P Dubyah on the th Hey I saw the menu that Nancy sent around Is she cooking on her own birthday Ol Easy Goin Cameron Sellers To Scott Laughlin erf ectcom cc Subject RE Drunken Brothers PM I am pretty sure our date is the th They are going on the th Cameron Sellers Vice President Business Development PERFECT Embarcadero Road Suite Palo Alto CA direct dial cell fax Original Message From Scott Laughlin mailto Sent Thursday November AM To Cc Subject Drunken Brothers Hey Im just wondering when are we slated to go see Woody Sean Nick and the boys Its coming up no Hope alls well BO Get Your Private Free Email from MSN Hotmail at Share information about yourself create your own public profile at

Fwd Darnthis another hint From Nancy Sellers Nancy obertMondavicom To Jeff Dasovich Cc Prentice Sellers Prentice Berkeley Subject Darn Date Thu Nov Importance high XMailer Internet Mail Service I cant believe Nina Simone was in town and we didnt go see her And there is a great sale in Oakland that has all the lovely Italian ceramics we are all so fond of It was in the paper Home Garden section yesterday San Leandro St Oakland Friday and Saturday It sounds awesome I to th street East to San Leandro Left North about feet Sale at rear of building Nancy phone fax Plus je bois mieux je chante
